'''奧斯卡·茂里西歐·莫卡多'''（{{lang-en|Oscar Mauricio Mercado}}，{{bd|1994年|12月16日|}}），為美國職棒大聯盟的外野手，目前效力於克里夫蘭守護者。他曾代表哥倫比亞棒球隊參加2017年世界棒球經典賽。
==職業生涯==
===聖路易紅雀===
[[2013年美國職棒大聯盟選秀|2013年美國職棒大聯盟選秀]]，紅雀隊在第2輪57順位選進莫卡多。<ref>{{cite web |first=Brendan |last=Meyer |url=https://www.stltoday.com/sports/baseball/professional/cardinal-beat/cardinals-draft-ss-oscar-mercado-in-second-round/article_cb4df973-7e87-5802-80b9-125558c47c2e.html |title=Cardinals draft SS Oscar Mercado in second round | Cardinal Beat |publisher=stltoday.com |date=June 6, 2013 |access-date=June 26, 2018 |archive-date=2021-01-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210130233247/https://www.stltoday.com/sports/baseball/professional/cardinal-beat/cardinals-draft-ss-oscar-mercado-in-second-round/article_cb4df973-7e87-5802-80b9-125558c47c2e.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>他後來也與紅雀簽約。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.tampabay.com/hometeam/blog/gaither-ss-oscar-mercado-accepts-15-million-deal-cardinals/17638/|title=Florida high school sports - Gaither SS Oscar Mercado accepts $1.5 million deal with Cardinals|work=Tampa Bay Times|access-date=March 11, 2017|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170729215529/http://www.tampabay.com/hometeam/blog/gaither-ss-oscar-mercado-accepts-15-million-deal-cardinals/17638/|archive-date=2017-07-29|dead-url=yes}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.mynews13.com//content/news/cfnews13/sports/article.html/content/news/articles/bhsn/2013/6/5/from_columbia_to_the.html|title=From Colombia to the U.S. to the majors, Gaither's Oscar Mercado ready for draft day|publisher=MyNews13|access-date=March 11, 2017|archive-date=2017-07-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170729233844/http://www.mynews13.com//content/news/cfnews13/sports/article.html/content/news/articles/bhsn/2013/6/5/from_columbia_to_the.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |author=Press Release |url=http://m.cardinals.mlb.com/news/article/50925152/cardinals-sign-second-round-draft-selection-oscar-mercado/ |title=Cardinals sign second-round Draft selection Oscar Mercado |publisher=Major League Baseball |access-date=July 22, 2017 |archive-date=2017-07-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170729213052/http://m.cardinals.mlb.com/news/article/50925152/cardinals-sign-second-round-draft-selection-oscar-mercado/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>

簽約後，莫卡多從新人聯盟起步。2014年，他升上高階新人聯盟。2015年至2016年，他分別升上1A和高階1A。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.stltoday.com/sports/baseball/professional/cardinals-minor-league-report-mercado-shifts-from-shortstop-to-outfield/article_05b2eefb-f5cb-5aeb-9fc9-de3b516f5b23.html |title=Cardinals minor league report: Mercado shifts from shortstop to outfield | St. Louis Cardinals |publisher=stltoday.com |access-date=July 22, 2017 |archive-date=2020-03-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200304124058/https://www.stltoday.com/sports/baseball/professional/cardinals-minor-league-report-mercado-shifts-from-shortstop-to-outfield/article_05b2eefb-f5cb-5aeb-9fc9-de3b516f5b23.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>

2017年，莫卡多代表哥倫比亞隊參加世界棒球經典賽。隨後他被升上2A，<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.ozarksfirst.com/sports/mercado-sets-record-in-9-1-cardinals-win/707175263 |title=Mercado Sets Record in 9-1 Cardinals Win - Story |publisher=OzarksFirst |date=May 4, 2017 |access-date=July 22, 2017 |archive-date=2018-06-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180612171216/http://www.ozarksfirst.com/sports/mercado-sets-record-in-9-1-cardinals-win/707175263 |dead-url=no }}</ref>最後他在2018年被升上3A。<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.milb.com/milb/news/pacific-coast-league-notebook-oscar-mercado-adjusting-for-memphis-redbirds/c-282826426 |title=PCL notes: Mercado's adjustments paying off |publisher=MiLB.com |access-date=June 26, 2018 |archive-date=2018-06-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180627005242/https://www.milb.com/milb/news/pacific-coast-league-notebook-oscar-mercado-adjusting-for-memphis-redbirds/c-282826426 |dead-url=no }}</ref>

===克里夫蘭印地安人===
2018年7月31日，紅雀隊用莫卡多向印地安人交易Conner Capel和Jhon Torres兩名小聯盟選手。<ref>{{cite web |author=Post-Dispatch store |url=https://www.stltoday.com/sports/baseball/professional/cardinal-beat/cardinals-trade-slick-fielding-center-fielder-mercado-to-cleveland-for/article_3cb360ba-50fe-5d63-b1e9-7322a7e80ec7.html |title=Cardinals trade slick-fielding center fielder Mercado to Cleveland for prospects | Cardinal Beat |publisher=stltoday.com |access-date=April 25, 2019 |archive-date=2018-12-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181203155115/https://www.stltoday.com/sports/baseball/professional/cardinal-beat/cardinals-trade-slick-fielding-center-fielder-mercado-to-cleveland-for/article_3cb360ba-50fe-5d63-b1e9-7322a7e80ec7.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>他也隨即被球隊指派到3A，<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.milb.com/player/index.jsp?player_id=640458#/career/R/hitting/2018/ALL|title=Oscar Mercado Stats, Highlights, Bio - MiLB.com Stats - The Official Site of Minor League Baseball|publisher=MiLB.com|access-date=October 6, 2018|archive-date=2020-10-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201001083810/http://www.milb.com/player/index.jsp?player_id=640458#/career/R/hitting/2018/ALL|dead-url=no}}</ref>隔年一樣從3A開季。<ref>{{cite web |author=Adam Jardy |url=https://www.dispatch.com/sports/20190404/clippers-season-preview--veteran-outfielders-seeking-return-to-big-leagues |title=Clippers season preview | Veteran outfielders seeking return to big leagues - Sports - The Columbus Dispatch - Columbus, OH |publisher=Dispatch.com |access-date=April 25, 2019 |archive-date=2020-02-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200226080621/https://www.dispatch.com/sports/20190404/clippers-season-preview--veteran-outfielders-seeking-return-to-big-leagues |dead-url=no }}</ref>

2019年5月14日，莫卡多登上大聯盟。<ref>{{cite web|author=Joe Noga|url=https://expo.cleveland.com/sports/g66l-2019/05/154504bf5e9257/oscar-mercado-set-to-join-cleveland-indians-heres-what-the-24yearold-of-brings-to-the-tribe.html|title=Oscar Mercado set to join Cleveland Indians: Here’s what the 24-year-old OF brings to the Tribe|publisher=cleveland.com|date=May 14, 2019|access-date=May 14, 2019|archive-date=2019-05-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190514150758/https://expo.cleveland.com/sports/g66l-2019/05/154504bf5e9257/oscar-mercado-set-to-join-cleveland-indians-heres-what-the-24yearold-of-brings-to-the-tribe.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.baseball-reference.com/boxes/CHA/CHA201905140.shtml|title=Cleveland Indians at Chicago White Sox Box Score, May 14, 2019|publisher=Baseball Reference|access-date=May 15, 2019|archive-date=2020-12-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201216054744/https://www.baseball-reference.com/boxes/CHA/CHA201905140.shtml|dead-url=no}}</ref>2020年，他出賽36場比賽，打擊率為1成28，並敲出1轟與6分打點。<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.mlb.com/player/oscar-mercado-640458?stats=career-r-hitting-mlb&year=2020 |title=存档副本 |access-date=2021-02-13 |archive-date=2020-10-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201009091742/https://www.mlb.com/player/oscar-mercado-640458?stats=career-r-hitting-mlb&year=2020 |dead-url=no }}</ref>2022年6月21日，球隊將莫卡多指定讓渡。
===費城費城人===
2022年6月27日，費城人從讓渡名單中選走莫卡多。<ref>https://www.nbcsports.com/philadelphia/phillies/phillies-claim-oscar-mercado-waivers-cleveland-guardians</ref>
